object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM metal.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM metal.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'ADM'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT  
		metal_ugs.source_name, 
		metal_ugs.load_type, 
		metal_ugs.id, 
		metal_ugs.agency_nup, 
		metal_ugs.sharedagency, 
		metal_ugs.created, 
		metal_ugs.modified, 
		current_batch.batch_id
FROM metal.adm_user_group_share metal_ugs
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
    metal_ugs.id,
    metal_ugs.created,
    metal_ugs.modified;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: o_src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5('source_name' || source_name || 
	'load_type' || load_type || 
	'o_user_group_share_datetime_created' || to_char(o_user_group_share_datetime_created) || 
	'o_user_group_share_datetime_modified' || to_char(o_user_group_share_datetime_modified) || 
	'o_user_group_share_id' || to_char(o_user_group_share_id) || 'o_user_group_share_agency_id' || to_char(o_user_group_share_agency_id) || 'o_user_group_share_sharedagency' || to_char(o_user_group_share_sharedagency)
    )

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
        user_group_share_row_id, 
        user_group_share_row_md5checksum, 
        user_group_share_id,  
  user_group_share_datetime_modified,
  user_group_share_row_effective_end_datetime	
    FROM bronze.adm_user_group_share
    where  user_group_share_row_effective_end_datetime	= '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
